      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "素数看似杂乱无章，其实藏着精巧的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "取任意底数 a，把它一次次自乘，再对素数 p 取余数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "当指数走到 p 减一时，余数总会回到 1，像素数留下的指纹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.05,
      "size": 48816,
      "text": "费马小定理说：若 p 是素数，且 a 不被 p 整除，则 a 的 p 减一次方模 p 恒等于 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "换个写法，对任意整数 a，都有 a 的 p 次方模 p 等于 a 本身。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "这是三百多年前费马发现的，简洁却极其深刻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "cycle",
      "line_id": "cyc-1",
      "filename": "cycle-cyc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/cycle-cyc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "看这张幂表：每一行是一个底数 a 的连续幂，对 p 取余。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "cycle",
      "line_id": "cyc-2",
      "filename": "cycle-cyc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/cycle-cyc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "余数不会无限增大，而是在有限的几个数里循环往复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "cycle",
      "line_id": "cyc-3",
      "filename": "cycle-cyc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/cycle-cyc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "循环的长度整除 p 减一，所以最后一列必然齐刷刷落回 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "test",
      "line_id": "test-1",
      "filename": "test-test-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/test-test-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "反过来想：如果 a 的 n 减一次方模 n 不等于 1，那 n 一定不是素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "test",
      "line_id": "test-2",
      "filename": "test-test-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/test-test-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "这就是费马素性测试，快到能在瞬间筛掉海量合数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "test",
      "line_id": "test-3",
      "filename": "test-test-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/test-test-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.18,
      "size": 50832,
      "text": "但它会被骗：卡迈克尔数如 561，明明是合数，却对所有互素底数都通过测试。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "选择不同的素数 p，看幂表的规模和循环怎样变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fermat-little/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "拖动底数 a，观察它的这一行如何总在最后一列停在 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fermat-little",
